Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:03.48,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Amazing. It's so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:06.64,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Singing on a stage this huge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:07.90,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,is like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.57,Main,AUDIENCE,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:13.58,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks to all of you, I'm finally standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:16.07,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll never forget this sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.12,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,May your hearts be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.76,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,eternally enchanted with smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:24.08,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Let's Komugication!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:47.73,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,Your rays of sunlight are \Ngiving me love heartburn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:52.82,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,It's giving me an off-season heatstroke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:58.60,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,You're always honest and too hard-working
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.41,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,I can't help but want to support you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:08.92,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,When you're tired and things get rough
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.82,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,You can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:16.18,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,call my name anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:22.34,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,I'll run to your side anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:27.19,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,I'll hear your voice sending a call of love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:32.69,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,On angel wings, your energy will rise and go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:37.86,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,You'll feel energy well up inside you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:43.52,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,So always remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.12,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,Mugi Mugi in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:50.96,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,The magic that connects hearts to hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.34,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:08.52,Main,ALARM,0,0,0,,Wakey, wakey, wakey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:12.02,Main,ALARM,0,0,0,,We've taken over this venue, wakey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:16.11,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I won't let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.94,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I won't forgive any evildoers \Nwho interfere with my concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:22.86,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Komugi Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.46,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I had that same dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:34.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Concerts are awesome, even in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:37.17,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But some weird guys appeared today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:40.01,yoshida clinic,SIGN,0,0,0,,Yoshida Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.01,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.01,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:45.01,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.44,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:47.18,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.86,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.77,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,What was all that banging\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I accidentally tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:56.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Anyway, I had another concert dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.50,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It was at the Tokyo Skydome,\Nmy greatest aspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:01.24,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I hope it comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.36,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:05.26,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,That'll never happen to a klutz like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.20,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Kokonacchi stands a better chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.16,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.76,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, but this time, some weird guys appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:13.34,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I hope that doesn't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:16.06,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I hope just the fun parts come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:20.51,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Just the fun parts? \NWouldn't that be a bit too convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.58,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But I just want the fun parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:27.10,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Hurry up and eat your breakfast. \NYou'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.27,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:29.77,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.68,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Thanks for doing this so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.02,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,No problem. We've known each other a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good morning, Dad and Shozo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.40,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.84,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Good morning, Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.54,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Did you hurt your back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.64,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,Perfect timing. Could you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.30,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,I feel like something good will \Nhappen when you stick them on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.66,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Energy injection!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.54,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,That stings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay, take care. I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.32,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan's full of energy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.32,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,Indeed. She's our poster child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.74,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.55,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:06.05,downtown mall,SIGN,0,0,0,,Downtown Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.73,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,She's our idol, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.32,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm Yoshida Komugi. 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:11.56,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sagittarius, blood type O.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.56,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:16.15,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My favorite food is Japanese sweets, \Nand there's no food I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.14,Main - Top,MAN,0,0,0,,Morning! You're full of energy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.36,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My strengths are my energy and health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.70,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:21.90,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My weaknesses are that I'm \Na bit clumsy and fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.16,Main - Top,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Good morning. I'm looking \Nforward to today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:21.90,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.08,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.92,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My best subject is music, \Nand my worst subjects are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:24.70,Main - Top,MAN,0,0,0,,Morning. Careful you don't trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.94,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:29.22,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,language arts, math, science, \Nsocial studies, English...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:26.82,Main - Top,MAN,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:29.06,Main - Top,MAN,0,0,0,,Her smile is a fount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:29.83,Main - Top,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.12,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,That's all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.12,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.46,Main - Top,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome. You're as cheerful as ever today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:34.18,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm an ordinary second-year \Nmiddle school student,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.25,let's komugication,SIGN,0,0,0,,Let's Komugication!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.25,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but I also do a bit of idol work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:43.11,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Komugi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:43.11,Title3,,0,0,0,,{\an1}R
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.11,Title1,,0,0,0,,Nurse Witch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:47.48,Main - Top,MISUZU,0,0,0,,Next time you're late, \NI'll use the iron claw on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:49.51,ep title,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,1)}The Birth of the Magical Nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.51,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:51.78,Main - Top,MISUZU,0,0,0,,Kisaragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.42,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.45,Main - Top,MISUZU,0,0,0,,Kisaragi Tsukasa-san is out working today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.64,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.77,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Anyway, I had that dream again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.90,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That concert dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:58.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:02.24,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But this time it got a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:06.03,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The concert was super fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:09.18,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You're so lucky. I wish I could \Nhave dreams like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:12.64,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm sure it would be fun if \Nwe could have the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.22,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Let's make that dream come true together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:15.79,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:19.47,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Let's have a concert together at \Nthe Tokyo Skydome someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.44,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Let's make it happen together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.24,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.18,Main,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Turn to page 114.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.64,Main,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Saionji-san, please start reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.39,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:39.10,Main - Top,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Those without the desire to improve \Nthemselves mentally are fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.50,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,This is Saionji Kokona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.08,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's an idol whose popularity \Nis on the rise right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.90,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And she's not just cute. \NShe can sing and dance, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.28,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's the perfect idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.82,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Lately she's started acting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:52.53,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's smart as well, and her grades \Nare always at the top of our year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.88,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's even the student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.33,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,In any case, she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.25,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's also kind and reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:03.52,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's as brilliant as the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:07.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.22,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's another masterpiece today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.35,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,How cute. Those eyebrows look tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:15.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,As usual, you have a unique perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.82,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm a fan of your mom's lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.35,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My mom will be happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Your lunch looks good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:24.36,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You're after my rolled omelets, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:26.70,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:27.69,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.45,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,So then, Kotaro said
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.95,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,you could probably hold a \Nconcert at the Tokyo Skydome,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.72,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but I could never do it \Neven if I stood on my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:37.45,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Isn't that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.74,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,So I'm thinking of practicing \Nstanding on my head starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:41.74,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.16,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You had rice on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.71,Main,TAMAKO,0,0,0,,Yo, yo, yo. Yo, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.24,Main,TAMAKO,0,0,0,,Looks like you're having \Nfun together today, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.32,Main,TAMAKO,0,0,0,,Let me borrow you two \Ncuties for a minute, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:55.04,Main,REI,0,0,0,,In other words, she's inviting \Nyou to play volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.28,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:56.97,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.48,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.98,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You'll play, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.50,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.23,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The student council is meeting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.50,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.73,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.26,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay! Work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:09.74,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.45,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The weather's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.48,Main,MITSUKI,0,0,0,,Today I'll show off my Super \NMiracle Hurricane Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.24,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sounds amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.56,Main,MAKI,0,0,0,,Then I'll return it with my \NHyper Silent Tornado Receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.71,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,That sounds awesome, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.36,Main,TAMAKO,0,0,0,,Serve, receive. Love, survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.44,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Even if the whole universe is against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.68,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.32,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Okay, cut. That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.06,Main,MITSUKI,0,0,0,,Hey, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.67,downtown mall,MISUZU,0,0,0,,{\fs17}Class Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:03.00,Main,MISUZU,0,0,0,,That's it for announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.79,Main,MISUZU,0,0,0,,Make sure you're not late tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.34,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Man, our teacher is ripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.14,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She should become a female pro wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.98,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Apparently she tried a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:15.84,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.60,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Thank goodness I caught up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.90,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Matsukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.16,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:25.66,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Yeah. You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.61,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Shooting's over and we're ahead \Nof schedule, so I came to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.44,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.16,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Komugi, good luck at your concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.80,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,A journey of a thousand miles \Nbegins with the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.02,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Today's concert will \Neventually lead to the Dome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:38.86,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.20,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,One step, two steps, three steps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:40.87,Main,BOTH,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.54,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.14,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.79,downtown park,TEXT,0,0,0,,Downtown Park
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.43,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:00.18,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yikes. You got all scratched up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.36,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,There, there. Poor bunny. \NThat must've hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.69,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.18,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:12.50,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You should be okay now. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.48,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Thanks, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.08,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.58,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I'm Usa-P. I choose you, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.37,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,H-He spoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:24.80,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,This kindness, this warmth, \Nthis care you gave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:27.37,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You're the girl I've been searching for, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.52,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,There's something I want you to do for me, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.17,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.84,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I want you to become a Legendary Girl, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:36.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Legendary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.56,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:41.31,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,A heroine of love and justice who fights \Nevil with the power of magic, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Love and justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.52,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:49.90,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.65,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Tombo-E Girl, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.07,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Tombo-E Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.50,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Tombo-E Girl is a Legendary Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.66,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,who uses her magical powers \Nto transform into an
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.46,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,incomprehensibly embarrassing \Noutfit to fight evil, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.95,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,The outfit is way too embarrassing for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.08,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,but Tombo-E Girl is granted great power
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.44,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,befitting of such an embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.60,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Pyo-pyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.64,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Wait up, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.44,daifuku drug store,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\c&H900f62&}Daifuku {\c&Hd23331&}Drugstore
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.94,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.69,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, you're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:38.96,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.60,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,All right, time to do this concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Mugi Mugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.95,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming today, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's cold out, so make sure \Nyou don't catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:52.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But if you think you might be \Ngetting sick, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.96,miracle cold drug,TEXT,0,0,0,,M{\c&H412cdc&}i{\c&H336eec&}r{\c&H65cb41&}a{\c&Hdbba2a&}c{\c&Ha15b29&}l{\c&H8b3173&}e {\c&H000000&}Cold Medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.96,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,This miracle drug works on fevers, \Nsore throats, and runny noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:59.18,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And today it's 50% off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.66,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,I'm getting one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.96,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Then I'm buying two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.10,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Well, I'm getting three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.81,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.08,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:09.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Now let's Komugication!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.04,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugication!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.82,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to attract customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:20.49,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Let's go! Jaa Jaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.20,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Tiger! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.56,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Cyber! Fiber!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.74,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Diver! Viber!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Jaa Jaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.87,Main - Top - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,In this great big world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:28.87,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.37,Main - Top - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,We're just one little pharmacy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.32,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.00,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.52,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:34.25,Main - Top - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But our spirit is the biggest in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.25,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,That's my, that's my, that's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.25,Main - Top - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And we offer sincere customer service
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.25,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.26,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,You were great today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.88,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,M-My back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.08,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.34,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Today's concert was great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.42,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Is your back okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.22,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Want Yu-nii to come pick you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.88,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:54.18,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Besides, Yuto's filming for his movie today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.84,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, right. With Kokona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.53,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,At this rate, it'll be another cold case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.53,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to solve this one, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.28,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Then show us what you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.32,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Cold Case Detective Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.26,Main,COACH,0,0,0,,Cut. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.50,Main,AD,0,0,0,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.74,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Here, Kokona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.04,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:18.66,Main,YUTA,0,0,0,,Here, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:19.55,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:22.10,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Today's filming is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.64,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,And for once, the director isn't being reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.62,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,These post-concert doll \Ncakes really hit the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Twinkly-pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.02,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.76,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can be Tombo-E Girl, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:42.11,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You could pull off that embarrassing outfit, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.49,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I don't want to wear your embarrassing outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.30,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You will, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:45.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.84,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You will, pyon! You will, pyon! You will, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.87,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.32,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You definitely will, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.56,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,What's wrong, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.84,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Earth does have tiny little creatures with
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.25,we can't show this,TEXT,0,0,0,,We can't show this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.25,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,black shiny carapaces and scurrying legs, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:04.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,C, C, C!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.78,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,"C"? Are they that scary, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.48,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I can't stand Cs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.34,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I can help you, pyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:14.36,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,but it won't be for free, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.02,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hurry! The C is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:20.02,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Yeah, pyon. That C sure is creeping closer, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.26,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,If you'll do as I ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.86,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,then I'd be willing to do you a favor too, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:28.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,If you save me, I'll become Tombo-E Girl \Nor whatever else you want me to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.03,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Really, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.60,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You're not lying, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:31.86,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:32.88,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You promise, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:36.72,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I promise! I can't take it! The C!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.04,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Got it, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Pyo-pyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wow, a jet spray?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.96,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,So, thanks for becoming Tombo-E Girl, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.70,Main,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,Komugi! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.72,Main,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,You're going to be in Kokona's movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.43,Main,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:57.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:02.08,Main,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,The director suddenly added a cute \Nmiddle-school girl character.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.86,Main,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,It's your lucky day, Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:07.34,Main - Top,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,Opportunities do come to those who work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.72,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:09.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't \Nspeak in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.20,Main - Top,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.70,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I promise, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.95,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,But you'd better keep your promise \Nto become Tombo-E Girl, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.36,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.24,Main,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,Have you memorized your lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:19.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,"He's going to kill me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.18,Main,MATSUKAWA,0,0,0,,Good! Now all you need is spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.64,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.06,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,What kind of person shouts out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.10,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.26,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:38.89,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm going to be in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll be appearing alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.40,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Really? This is your first movie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.02,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:48.65,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Shozo-san threw out \Nhis back at today's concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,so give him a fresh cold pack after his bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:53.78,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Got it. That old man's got some energy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Pyon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Nyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.14,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,And... action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.00,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The universally popular singer Jazz Chanson
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.00,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,boarded the passenger ship \Nand committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:24.65,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.95,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The culprit fabricated his alibi by changing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.15,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,from red to blue to yellow pajamas, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.29,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Film.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:42.08,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,No question, pyon! I sense a monster, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.29,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.29,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's close by, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.30,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.86,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm going to the bathroom, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Zoom, zoom, zoom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Twinkly-pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.59,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.01,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Take this, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.16,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What is this? It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:02.60,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's time to Chan-G into \NTombo-E Girl, beat the monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.84,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,and collect the Fan-C Card, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.92,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Chan-G? Monster? Fan-C Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:11.92,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,A monster was born when an evil-sealing \NFan-C Card was stuck on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.53,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,so you need to Chan-G into \NTombo-E Girl and fight it, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.53,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Now repeat this incantation after me, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.26,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Parasol shiny chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.54,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Shiny lovely tenipole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.38,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Parasol shiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:25.54,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.04,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Read this, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.04,let's komugication - Copy,TEXT,0,0,0,,Parasol shiny (singsong) \NChloroform (down) \NShiny lovely (rising!) \NTenipole (extend)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Parasol shiny chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:33.44,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Shiny lovely tenipole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.68,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Film, film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.90,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Cut! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.18,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.32,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Film, film, film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.40,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Suffer even more, film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.11,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Film, film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.44,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It's awfully noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.37,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Where did Komugi go, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.68,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Go next door and tell them to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.28,Main,AD,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.12,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.13,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Where on earth did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.46,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Film, film.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.51,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.26,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Who are you, film?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.89,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll cast a smiling spell on your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.14,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,This Magical Nurse may be unmotivated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:24.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but I'll arrive with energy nonetheless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:28.00,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,This is the birth of Tombo-E Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:31.40,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Now watch how she Chan-Ged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.48,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Parasol shiny chloroform!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:37.30,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Chanting it deciphers the code\Nprogrammed into the incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:37.30,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Shiny lovely tenipole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.02,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It scans Komugi's entire body while
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:41.64,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,simultaneously sending the \Ndata to the Fanta-C World.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:45.00,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It's instantly analyzed, and \NChan-G rays are fired at Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.24,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,The rays turn Komugi's caring heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:51.39,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,into Amazoni-N Cells, activating \Ntheir maximum Tombo-E potential
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:56.08,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,and reconstructing her body and costume,\Ncompleting the Chan-G.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:58.96,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,On average, the transformation\Ntakes 0.02 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,This is super cute. This isn't embarrassing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.43,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,But it's so embarrassing, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:09.19,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,And don't go changing Tombo-E Girl's name, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.74,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But it's not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:13.94,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Stop ignoring me, film!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.69,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,I'll show you my strength, film.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.99,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Film, film, film, film...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.50,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Film!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.83,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Ew! They're creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.71,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,That's my Tombo-E Girl, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:41.72,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Then I'll turn you into \Nsomething embarrassing, film.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:42.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:52.82,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Beat him with your Kap-U Kap-U Bulgy Beam, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:55.04,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? That's a lame name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.32,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Call it whatever you want, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.68,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,As long as your heart is in it, it'll work, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.36,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:03.28,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,The Kap-U Kap-U Bulgy Beam is fired
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.70,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,by drawing the water produced \Nby the change in osmotic pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.31,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,of the Amazoni-N Cells to the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.24,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,and launching it at meteoric speeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:14.16,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It's a special attack that purifies enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:16.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You can treat your wounds with medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.50,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but only death can cure evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.64,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Nurse Medical
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Stardust!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.90,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Film!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.53,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,It's not digital technology that won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.68,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,It's film!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.29,film camera monster,TEXT,0,0,0,,Film Camera\NMonster
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.29,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.34,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,We got a Fan-C Card, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.56,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,All right, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:58.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,So this is a Fan-C Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.52,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.18,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My scene is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:06.93,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:09.06,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Komugi, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.62,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:11.94,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.19,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.72,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? What about my role?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.18,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.82,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, that was a \Npassionate performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:22.95,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,I'd hire you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.70,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.44,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Want to get dinner after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:31.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:31.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I... I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.16,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Today was a crazy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:08.42,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It was sort of fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:10.14,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And my outfit was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.43,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You see, pyon? It's a job worth doing, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:15.06,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm not doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.44,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I missed my first movie appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:21.70,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,But there are 108 Fan-C Cards in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.66,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,If you quit before you're done, the monsters' \Ncurse will turn you into what you hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:29.32,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,In your case, you'll become a "C,"\Nso you can't quit now, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:31.74,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? Nobody told me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:34.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And why are you in the bath with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:44.67,Next Time,TEXT,0,0,0,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:36.04,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Komugi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:39.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The three major grains of the \Nworld are wheat, rice, and corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:43.02,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,So shouldn't we be having raw \Nwheat, raw rice, and raw corn?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.67,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But I prefer grilled corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:47.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The next episode is "Stalker?! \NKokona-chan's Close Call!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:49.97,next ep title,TEXT,0,0,0,,Stalker?!\NKokona-chan's Close Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:49.97,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,All together, now! Let's Komugication!